ain, but not display, distribute, or perform, server copies of the  Content that has been removed or deleted. You shall not download any  Content unless there is a “download” button or similar link displayed. </span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>HM  does not control the Content posted to the HM website, as such, HM does  not guarantee the accuracy, integrity or quality of such Content. HM  shall not be liable in any way for any Content, including but not  limited to, liability for errors or omissions in any Content or for any  loss or damage incurred as a result of the use of any Content posted,  emailed or otherwise transmitted using the HM website.</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>While  HM will use reasonable efforts to back up the Content and any other  data of the HM website and make it available in case of loss or  deletion, HM has no responsibility or liability for the deletion or  failure to store such Content maintained or transmitted by the HM  website.</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>HM  does not endorse any Content submitted to the HM website by any user,  or any opinion, comment, recommendation or advice expressed in the HM  website. HM does not endorse or promote racism, bigotry, hatred, or  physical harm of any kind against another group or individual, and does  not discriminate, incite or advocate harassment of any group or  individual.</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The  HM website, trademarks, service marks, products and services names,  logos, slogans, and images in the HM website are subject to copyright  and other intellectual property rights owned by or licensed to HM  (hereinafter “HM Intellectual Property”). You are not allowed to modify  HM Intellectual Property or to use it in a manner that is inconsistent  with the HM Purpose.</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span><br /><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>\r\n\r\n  <a