ous agreement. Regardless of any translation to  other language that may be available of these HM Terms of Use, Heard  Mentality\'s Privacy Policy and Heard Mentality\'s Guidelines, the  original version in English shall prevail. The HM Terms of Use and the  relationship between HM and You shall be governed and interpreted by the  applicable laws and courts of the province of Quebec and Canada,  without respect to its conflict of laws, waiving, thus, any other forum  to which You may be entitled to by reason of your present or future  domiciles or for any other reason. </span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Any  provision of these HM Terms of Use, Heard Mentality\'s Privacy Policy,  and Heard Mentality\'s Guidelines that may be determined by competent  authority to be prohibited or unenforceable in any jurisdiction shall,  as to that jurisdiction, be ineffective to the extent of the prohibition  or unenforceability, without invalidating the remaining provisions of  these HM Terms of Use, Heard Mentality\'s Privacy Policy and Heard  Mentality\'s Guidelines which shall remain in full force and effect.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>These HM Terms of Use may not be transferred or assigned by You, but they may be assigned by HM without any restriction.</span></p>','<p><a name=\"acceptance\"></a><h1>Your Acceptance</h1></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Please  read carefully the content of this document related to your use of the  Heard Mentality website. By logging in or using the Heard Mentality  website and the services provided through the Heard Mentality website  You agree to these HM Terms of Use, Heard Mentality\'s Privacy Policy and  Heard Mentality\'s Guidelines. If You do not agree with the foregoing,  please do not use the Heard Mentality website. </span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>','',1358594399,3);
